article.headline: Blanton scores 24, Eastern Kentucky downs FGCU 90-82
article.description: — Devontae Blanton's 24 points helped Eastern Kentucky defeat FGCU 90-82 on Wednesday night.
article.linkText: Blanton scores 24, Eastern Kentucky downs FGCU 90-82

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Michael Moreno drains the long 3-pointer) 2024/02/08 ESHEET

article.story: RICHMOND, Ky. -- — Devontae Blanton's 24 points helped Eastern Kentucky defeat FGCU 90-82 on Wednesday night. Blanton was 9 of 12 shooting and 5 of 5 from the free throw line for the Colonels (13-10, 9-1 Atlantic Sun Conference). Isaiah Cozart scored 21 points and added 13 rebounds and four blocks. Leland Walker shot 4 for 10, including 2 for 4 from beyond the arc to finish with 12 points. Isaiah Thompson finished with 17 points for the Eagles (10-15, 4-6). Zach Anderson added 16 points and three blocks for FGCU. Dallion Johnson also put up 14 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
